[normal]there are 
[normal]security issues.  
[normal]There has to be a firm, underpinning set of data that we can operate the country on.  The model there needs to be revisited in terms of what the wider economic benefits are.  Rufus is right that there has been progress, but I think more needs to be done in some of those areas.  
[normal]Q42 [bold]&#xa0; 
