[normal] it is automatically licensed under the open government licence.  
[normal]Otherwise,
[normal] there is this silly thing where you get the data
[normal],
[normal] but you are not allowed to give it to anyone else without permission.  There is this weird thing where you get something under FOI and you are not allowed to give it to others, which is bizarre.  
[normal]Q46 [bold]&#xa0; 
